            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Abalone Flow 1.0.0</h2>
                <p>First public release. Local dictation for macOS — hold a key, talk, release, your words appear at the cursor. All on-device, nothing leaves your machine.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Push-to-talk and double-tap hands-free on any shortcut key</li>
                    <li>Live waveform overlay while recording</li>
                    <li>On-device Whisper transcription</li>
                    <li>History with audio retention, paste-last shortcut, clipboard preservation</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Requires macOS 14 (Sonoma) or later.</p>
            ]]></description>
